<!--
/**
* @Description: 院端-病种分析（DRG支付、省卫健委DRG、DIP支付）-异常病种监控分析
* @Description: 费用分析、总权重分析、效率分析-病组、病种-汇总表
* @Author: XuShuai xushuai1@palline.cn
* @Date: 2025-05-27 19:26:41
* @LastEditors: XuShuai xushuai1@palline.cn
* @LastEditTime: 2025-05-28 13:40:41
* @FilePath: src/component/diseaseAnalysis/hospital/diseaseAnalysis/abnormal-disease-monitor-analysis/AbnormalAnalysisDiseaseSummaryTable.vue
* Copyright (c) 2025 by palline, All Rights Reserved.
*/
-->
<template>
  <doms-con-h360
    :showHeader="false"
    :hideBox="true">
    <PlModulePanel
      v-bind="getModelBindData"
      @cell-click="cellClick"
      @filter-change="onFilterChange"
      @sort-change="onSortChange"
      @page-change="onPageChange">
    </PlModulePanel>
  </doms-con-h360>
</template>

<script>
import DomsConH360 from '@/doms-ui/component/container/con-h360.vue'
import PlModulePanel from '@/component/tool/PlModulePanel.vue'
import {mapGetters, mapMutations, mapState} from 'vuex'
import PlGridTable from '@/component/tool/PlGridTable.vue'
import {
  fetchAbnormalAnalysisTableDip
} from '@/api/hospital/diseaseAnalysis/abnormalDiseaseMonitorAnalysisDip'
import {
  fetchAbnormalAnalysisTableDrg
} from '@/api/hospital/diseaseAnalysis/abnormalDiseaseMonitorAnalysisDrg'
import {
  checkDateParamsValid
} from '@/util/help/components/validator/params/checkDateParamsValid'
import {
  checkParamsValid
} from '@/util/help/components/validator/params/checkParamsValid'

export default {
  name: 'AbnormalAnalysisDiseaseSummaryTable',
  components: {PlGridTable, PlModulePanel, DomsConH360},
  data() {
    return {
      loading: false,
      columns: [],
      tableData: [],

      currentSort: {field: 'growth', order: 'desc',},
      sortObj: {},
      filter: {},
      totalPage: 0,
      pageSize: 100,
      currentPage: 1,
      currentRowCode: '',
      currentRowDiseaseName: '',

    }
  },
  computed: {
    ...mapState('abnormalDiseaseMonitorAnalysisStore', [
      'tabName',
      'commonRequestParams',
      'currenRouteName',
    ]),
    ...mapGetters('textDescription', [
      'getIfDip',
    ]),

    /** 计算：汇总表格 ref 实例 */
    getSummaryTableRef() {
      return this.$refs.summaryTable?.$refs?.moduleTable?.vxeTable
    },

    /** 计算 表头排序配置 */
    getSortConfig() {
      return {
        remote: true,
        defaultSort: this.currentSort,
      }
    },

    getModelBindData() {
      return {
        type: 'table',
        title: this.tabName,
        loading: this.loading,
        columns: this.columns,
        data: this.tableData,

        ref: 'summaryTable',
        showBorder: false,
        height: 380,
        'show-overflow': true,
        'row-class-name': this.setRowClassName,
        'row-config': {isCurrent: false, isHover: true,},
        'column-config': {resizable: true,},
        'filter-config': {remote: true,},
        'sort-config': this.getSortConfig,
        'pager-config': {
          total: this.totalPage,
          pageSize: this.pageSize,
          currentPage: this.currentPage,
          pagerCount: 5,
          pageSizes: [100, 200, 300, 400, 500],
        },

      }
    },

    /** 计算：请求参数 */
    getRequestParams() {
      return Object.assign(
        {...this.commonRequestParams,},
        {
          ...this.filter,
          ...this.sortObj,
          pageNum: this.currentPage,
          pageSize: this.pageSize,
        },
      )
    },

    /** 计算：请求方法 */
    getRequestMethods() {
      return this.getIfDip
        ? fetchAbnormalAnalysisTableDip
        : fetchAbnormalAnalysisTableDrg
    },

    /** 计算：请求是否合法 */
    getIfRequestValid() {
      return (newRequestParams) => checkDateParamsValid({date: newRequestParams,}) &&
        checkParamsValid({
          params: newRequestParams,
          checkingKeys: ['drgGroupType'],
          invalidKeys: [null, undefined, '']
        }) &&
        // 切换tab，验证当前路由名称是否一致
        this.$route.name === this.currenRouteName
    },

  },
  watch: {
    'getRequestParams': {
      immediate: true,
      deep: true,
      handler(newV) {
        if(!this.getIfRequestValid(newV)) {return}

        this.requestTableData()
      },
    },

  },
  methods: {
    ...mapMutations('abnormalDiseaseMonitorAnalysisStore', [
      'updateSummaryRowData',
    ]),

    setRowClassName({row, /* rowIndex, $rowIndex */}) {
      return this.rowCode === row.code
        // 全局样式-选中当前行高亮
        ? 'vxe-row-current'
        : ''
    },

    /** 响应数据处理 */
    async responseDataHandler({columns, data, total}) {
      this.columns = columns
      this.tableData = data
      this.totalPage = total

      if(this.tableData.length === 0) {return}
      // 默认点击选中第一项
      this.cellClick({row: this.tableData[0],})
      await this.$nextTick()
      await this.sleep(0)

      this.getSummaryTableRef
        ?.sort(this.currentSort.field, this.currentSort.order)
    },

    /** 请求表格数据 */
    async requestTableData() {
      this.loading = true
      const [err, {code, data: {columns, data, total},} = {}] =
        await this.to(this.getRequestMethods(this.getRequestParams))
          .finally(() => {this.loading = false})
      if(err || code !== '0') {return}
      await this.responseDataHandler({columns, data, total},)
    },

    cellClick({row}) {
      this.currentRowCode = row.code
      this.currentRowDiseaseName = row.name
      this.updateSummaryRowData(row)
    },

    onFilterChange($event) {
      this.currentPage = 1
      this.filter = {}
      const filterList = $event.filterList
      filterList.map((v) => {
        this.filter[v.field] = v.datas[0].value
      })
    },

    onSortChange() {},

    onPageChange() {},

  },
}
</script>
